title: Man, 25, dies after being electrocuted in roof of a house | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share Emotional friends of the deceased man can be seen comforting one another as a paramedic also embraces the man. SafeWork NSW confirmed to Daily Mail Australia that they had been notified and inspectors were attending the site. Dramatic footage from the scene shows paramedics and fire crew working desperately in the roof of the house Roof tiles have been removed from the house exposing the timber beams, allowing access for the emergency services The man was found in cardiac arrest by the paramedics who attempted to revive the man but to no avail A friend of the deceased puts his hands on his head in disbelief as to what has just unfolded Emotional friends of the deceased man can be seen comforting one another as a paramedic also embraces the man.
